title: BSFZ-Arena
text: The BSFZ-Arena (new official name) is a multi-use <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="Maria%20Enzersdorf">Maria Enzersdorf</a> - Südstadt, <a href="Austria">Austria</a> (Johann Steinböck-Straße). It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the home ground of <a href="VfB%20Admira%20Wacker%20M%C3%B6dling">VfB Admira Wacker Mödling</a>. The stadium holds 10,600.
